      "value": "<p>Sometimes called shackle-blade, this double weapon is a katana with a spiked chain at its end, and can be used as either or both. A hansori can be wielded one-handed or two-handed. Using it as a double weapon counts as though you had a light weapon in your off-hand. Having proficiency in the hansori does not automatically make you proficient in the katana or spiked chain.</p>",
